Waspinator got blown up by the attacks (again) and his head flew
through the air and landed next to Megatron "Waspinator haveing REALLY
bad day"

The light shard cut into Quickstrikes armored torso cutting a hole
into it (the light shards cut stuff right?) "These guy's thougher then
I though!" he said then heard Megatron's order "If you say so" he
gathered an energy blast in his snake mouth and launched it at the
base's shilds.

"To the destruction of the enemy's colony!" Inferno exclaimed
launching a rocket and a few energy blasts at the base's shilds.
